            "ColorTextInfoList": []
        },
        {
            "Name": "",
            "Text": "于是我便照着秋川理事长所说，\n蹑手蹑脚地走了进去……",
            "ChoiceDataList": [],
            "ColorTextInfoList": []
        },
        {
